title: Bonanza 31 Dark Star (1960) Full Length Western

sources.title: Bonanza 31 Dark Star (1960) Full Length Western
sources.description:
Joe romances a Gypsy named Tirza (Susan Harrison) who thinks she's a witch. Her people also believe she's bewitched and she's banished from the community.
 
Director: Lewis Allen
Writer: Anthony Lawrence
Stars: Dan Blocker, Michael Landon, Lorne Greene 
Genres: Classics, Cult, TV, Western
